FBIS4-33124 "drlat106_n_94003" FBIS-LAT-94-106 Daily Report 2 Jun 1994 Chile Israel's Shim'on Peres Addresses Congress Israel's Shim'on Peres Addresses Congress PY0206032194 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen Internacional in Spanish 0100 GMT 2 Jun 94 PY0206032194 Santiago Television Nacional de Chile Imagen Internacional Spanish BFN [Text] In an address to Congress, Israeli Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres, who is making a state visit to Chile, stated that reaching a peace settlement with the Palestinians is a moral option that has to be supported by the international community. Peres concluded his visit to our country today.
